name: Mary Kewrell
description:
I am an affectionate, loyal and sensitive woman. I like to read, to go for a walk, to travel and to go to the cinema. I like to go out with my friends and to have a good time with them.
I am looking for an ambitious, intelligent man, of athletic and generous constitution. I would also like to find an honest and romantic person that will always put smiles on my face.
